name: “End - Begin" by potentialight.art
description: @potentialight Hicetnunc Exclusive ✦ 2020 px x 2020 px 444x444 edition.  ⦿ “End - Begin” is about the importance of endings and new beginnings. In order for something new to begin, something old has to end. In order for the phoenix to rise from the ashes, the phoenix has to first burn. Understanding the natural ebb and flow of life, the death and rebirth.  Who were you before you were born? Take this moment to breathe deep in your belly, hold that breath, and exhale.
